Hard Mode == count_left_for_easy_mode=0
Simple Downselect One Letter = count_left_for_easy_mode=1 with the downselect function
Simple Downselect Two Letter = count_left_for_easy_mode=2 with the downselect function
Weighted Downselect One Letter = count_left_for_easy_mode=1 with the weighted_downselect function
Weighted Downselect Two Letter = count_left_for_easy_mode=2 with the weighted_downselect function
